189
00:08:04,419 --> 00:08:06,259
But it’s not just Trump’s trash talk

190
00:08:06,259 --> 00:08:09,129
that’s throwing Chinese officials for a
loop.

191
00:08:09,129 --> 00:08:10,969
Last week Trump suggested that maybe

192
00:08:10,969 --> 00:08:15,540
America should consider rejoining the TPP
trade deal—

193
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:18,490
which he had rejected last year as a bad deal.

194
00:08:18,490 --> 00:08:22,300
But it is good as a way to put pressure on
China.

195
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:24,240
And there are signs that the Chinese Communist
Party

196
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,680
could be caving to the pressure.

197
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,840
Chinese leader Xi Jinping recently made a
speech

198
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:32,740
pledging to open up the Chinese economy and
cut tariffs.

199
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:34,900
Although Xi’s speech was also pretty similar

200
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:37,270
to one he made last year, so it’s unclear

201
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:39,070
whether it means the Chinese Communist Party

202
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:40,940
will actually make any changes.

203
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:44,070
It could just be more talk.

204
00:08:44,070 --> 00:08:46,510
Of course China’s foreign ministry wants
you to know

205
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:48,320
that if there are changes,

206
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,550
pressure has nothing to do with it.

207
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,550


208
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:53,150
"I can definitely tell you that China’s
announcement

209
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:55,940
of the significant initiatives on further
opening up

210
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:58,750
is not related to the current economic and
trade conflicts

211
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:01,100
between China and the United States.”

212
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,560
Absolutely not.

213
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:05,070
It’s probably because Donald Trump and Xi
Jinping

214
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:07,680
are such great friends.

215
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,850
Like Pooh Bear and Tigger.

216
00:09:08,850 --> 00:09:11,570
I know they said Obama was Tigger.

217
00:09:11,570 --> 00:09:14,530
But really, Trump is the right color.

